{"tid":1335180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠：暴力衝擊的人最終會自在自受","createTime":"2019-07-20T11:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T11:47:55.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a12eabffdebe007626dc70661eb00be8088840d1","tid":1335180,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"建制派下午在金鐘發起「守護香港」集會，《基本法》委員會副主任譚惠珠在添馬公園的集會上呼籲示威者不要騷擾商家，不要阻別人做生意，不要影響服務業的飯碗。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠指出，香港是有活力生活鍊，一環影響一環，暴力衝擊和網上欺凌的人最終會自作自受。<br />\n<br />\n她又稱，如果社會失去包容，社會各行各業都會受打擊，要守護香港，否則不論下一代的人都要承受香港經濟損失，每個人都要付出代價。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠續稱，無論房屋、教育問題都要解決，但要和平表達意見，不是在街上打交就可解決，否則這一代、下一代都要付出代價。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2196504/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2196504%2F&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4gZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9a88b9d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2196504/</a>"},{"pid":"115f48d4a34d05dce9e722f347aa15b2a3619544","tid":1335180,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:44:21.000Z","msg":"活力生活鍊係咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caeabb2e2b3344216281440e85729113da558da9","tid":1335180,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:46:30.000Z","msg":"一齊慘 一齊受<br />\n唔好以為我地難過嘅時候你地會好過<br />\n你地都只會一齊慘 一齊受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d93d0d8521b8c2c3a80031494aba5bdcf46873","tid":1335180,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}